thread.title: Harvest Festival and Crafts Fair

title: Harvest Festival and Crafts Fair
text:
Harvest Festival and Crafts Fair Tools 
Story Published: Oct 7, 2015 at 2:33 PM EDT Story Updated: Oct 7, 2015 at 2:33 PM EDT 
Sunday, October 11th Open to the Public Free Admission 
119 Main Street, Sackets Harbor, NY 
1 19 West Main Street 
Come and enjoy the family fun at the Sackets Harbor Harvest Fest and get a start on your holiday shopping. A great place to find those unique gifts with many handcrafted and original pieces including pottery, ceramics, jewelry, soap, note cards, prints, silk and works of art. You must be an AANNY member to participate as a vendor. Contact: Donna Strejlau obsoffic@yahoo.com 315-778-4500
